{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"317740b560","title":"致林彪等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6ae29d9015","index":0,"year":1936,"month":4,"day":17,"articleId":"317740b560"}],"tags":[{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"97a764cb4b","type":"paragraph","text":"致林彪等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"317740b560"},{"id":"64eff872d5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年4月17日）林、楚，宋一、河东游击队张克来、涂则生、萧克（萧望东）、张国华有信来，他们情形频好，收缴了十支枪及一些手榴弹、梭镜、马刀，共有人数二百七十名，与我宋支队在克城镇见了面，现尚黑龙关附近行动威胁关敌侧后。二、责成你们在大宁、蒲县、永和区域，创造一个三百人左右的游击支队，如同河东支队模样，配备干部和武装，以便而后你们向另一区域移动时，增加普西南北为苏区的力量。三、吉县县长及民团首领送信给我们，以派去太原活动","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"317740b560"},{"id":"24d2884091","type":"paragraph","text":"彭毛杨","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"317740b560"},{"id":"4cff4f6dcc","type":"paragraph","text":"十七日十八时[]这是毛泽东和红军第一方面军司令员彭德怀、政治部主任杨尚昆给第一方面军第一军团军团长林彪、政治要员爱荣臻，第二十八军军长宋时轮","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"317740b560"}],"page":{"id":"27fe1ae564","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"317740b560","start":392,"end":392}}}},"__N_SSG":true}